{"title_page": "Priyanka Sarkar", "text_new": "{{Use dmy dates|date=August 2014}}\n{{Infobox person\n| name        = Priyanka Sarkar\n| native_name = \u09aa\u09cd\u09b0\u09bf\u09af\u09bc\u09be\u0999\u09cd\u0995\u09be \u09b8\u09b0\u0995\u09be\u09b0\n| image       = \n| alt         = \n| caption     = Priyanka in 2019 \n| birth_name  =\n| birth_date  = <!-- Birth date has been contested. Do not add without providing a reliably published source with a reputation for editorial oversight. -->\n| birth_place = [[Kolkata]]\n| nationality = [[India]]n\n| other_names = \n| occupation  = [[Actress]], [[Model (people)|model]]\n| known_for   = \n| children    =  Shohoj Banerjee (b. 2013)\n| spouse      = [[Rahul Banerjee (actor)|Rahul Banerjee]] (2010\u20132017)\n}}\n'''Priyanka Sarkar''' is a [[Bengali language|Bengali]] film and television actress.<ref name=\"Priyanka Sarkar filmography\">{{cite web|title=Priyanka Sarkar filmography|url=http://www.gomolo.com/about-priyanka-sarkar/314683|publisher=Gomolo|accessdate=13 August 2012}}</ref> Her first successful film was ''[[Chirodini Tumi Je Amar]]'' (2008) directed by [[Raj Chakraborty]].<ref name=\"Actress Priyanka Sarkar profile\">{{cite web|title=Actress Priyanka Sarkar profile|url=http://www.kolkatabengalinfo.com/2011/04/actress-priyanka-sarkar-profile-family.html|publisher=Kolkata Bengali info|accessdate=13 August 2012}}</ref> She was married to actor [[Rahul Banerjee (actor)|Rahul Banerjee]].<ref>{{Cite web | title = Rahul is perfect: Priyanka | last = Ganguly | first = Ruman | work = The Times of India | date = 13 November 2010 | accessdate = 2016-08-18 | url = http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/bengali/movies/news/Rahul-is-perfect-Priyanka/articleshow/6942158.cms }}</ref>\n\n==Filmography==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|+Key\n| {{dagger|alt=Films that have not yet been released}}\n| Denotes films that have not yet been released\n|}\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"width:67%;\"\n|- \n! Year\n! F