kpit]]''\n| Afreen Hamidi\n| [[Kamaleshwar Mukherjee]]\n| [[Dev (Bengali actor)|Dev]], [[Koel Mullick]], [[Rukmini Maitra]]\n|-\n| 2018 \n| ''[[Kaya-The Mystery Unfold]]''\n|\n| [[Rajib Chowdhury]]\n| [[Raima Sen]], [[Kaushik Sen]]\n|-\n| 2018 \n| ''[[Hoyto Manush Noy]]''\n|\n| Koustav Bhattacharya and Arunava Gangopadhyay\n| [[Biswajit Chakraborty]], [[Supriyo Dutta]]\n|-\n| 2018\n| ''[[Kabir (2018 film)|Kabir]]''\n| Damayanti \n| [[Aniket Chattopadhyay]]\n| [[Dev (Bengali actor)|Dev]], [[Rukmini Maitra]]\n|-\n| 2018 \n| ''[[E Tumi Kemon Tumi]]''\n|\n| [[Nehal Dutta]]\n| [[Labani Sarkar]], [[Rezwan Rabbani Sheikh]]\n|-\n| 2018 \n| ''[[Sultan:The Saviour]]''\n| Disha\n| [[Raja Chanda]]\n| [[Jeet (actor)|Jeet]], [[Bidya Sinha Saha Mim]]\n|-\n|2018\n| ''[[Bhagshesh]]''\n|\n| [[Rema Bose]]\n| [[Soumitra Chattopadhyay]], [[Malabika Sen]], [[Subhamita Banerjee]]\n|-\n|2018 \n| ''[[Aaleya]]''\n|\n| [[Dr. Humayun Kabir]]\n| [[Tanushree Chakraborty]], [[Saayoni Ghosh]], [[Kaushik Ganguly]], [[Kharaj Mukherjee]]\n|-\n|2018 \n| ''[[Crisscross (2018)|Crisscross]]''\n| Suzy\n| [[Birsa Dasgupta]]\n| [[Jaya Ahsan]], [[Mimi Chakraborty]], [[Nusrat Jahan]], [[Sohini Sarkar]]\n|-\n| 2018\n| ''[[Byomkesh Gotro]]''\n| Emily\n| [[Arindam Sil]]\n| [[Abir Chatterjee]], [[Sohini Sarkar]], [[Rahul Banerjee (actor)|Rahul Banerjee]], [[Arjun Chakrabarty|Arjun Chakraborty]]\n|-\n| 2018\n| style=\"background:#FFFFCC;\"| ''[[Andar Kahini]]'' {{dagger|alt=Films that have not yet been released}}\n|\n| Arnab Middya\n| [[Soumitra Chattopadhyay]], [[Saayoni Ghosh]], Sumit Samaddar, Rajesh Sharma\n|-\n| 2018\n| style=\"background:#FFFFCC;\"| ''[[Neelanjana]]'' {{dagger|alt=Films that have not yet been released}}\n| Neelanjana\n| [[Orko Sinha]]\n| Mainak Banerjee, [[Orko Sinha]]\n|-\n| 2019\n| ''[[Bibaho Obhijaan]]''\n| Malati\n| [[Birsa Dasgupta]]\n| [[Anirban Bhattacharya]], [[Ankush Hazra]], [[Rudranil Ghosh]], [[Sohini Sarkar]], [[Nusrat Faria]]\n|-\n| 2019\n| ''[[Bornoporichoy]]''\n| \n| [[Mainak Bhowmick]]\n| [[Jisshu Sengupta]], [[Abir Chatterjee]]<ref>{{cite tweet|user=taran_adarsh| author=Taran Adarsh|date=21 February  2019|number=1098463916722536448?s=19|title=Abir Chatterjee, Jisshu U Sengupta and Priyanka Sarkar... First look poster of #Bengali film #Bornoporichoy... Directed by Mainak Bhaumik... Music by Anupam Roy... June/July 2019 release. #SVF https://t.co/5I9y6KBGo4}}</ref>\n|}\n\n== Television ==\n* ''Aastha''\n* ''Khela''\n* ''Nana Ranger Dinguli''\n* ''Ebar Jalsha Rannaghare''\n* ''Mahanayak''\n* ''Ebar Jalsha Rannaghare'' (season 2)\n* ''Abhyamangal'' [Mahalaya Special TV Program For [[Star Jalsha]] ]\n* ''Sun Bangla Super Family'' [Reality Game Show For [[Sun Bangla]] ]\n\n== Web Series ==\n* ''Ghostana''\n* ''Hello'' (2017)\n* ''Hello 2'' (2018-2019)\n\n==Awards==\n{| border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"4\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin: 1em 1em 1em 0; background: #f9f9f9; border: 1px #aaa solid; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 95%;\"\n|- bgcolor=\"#CCCCCC\" align=\"center\"\n! Year !! Award !!  Category !! Project !! Result || References\n|-\n| 2008 || [[Anandalok Puraskar]] || Best Actress || ''[[Chirodini Tumi Je Amar]]'' || {{won}} ||\n|-\n| 2016 || [[Star Jalsha awards]] || Best Show || ''[[Ebar Jalsha Rannaghare]]'' ||{{won}} ||\n|-\n| 2017 || [[Star Jalsha awards]] || Best Anchor || ''[[Ebar Jalsha Rannaghare Season 2]] ||{{won}} ||\n|-\n| 2017 || [[Uttam Kalaratna Award]] || Best Actress || For Various Films || {{won}} ||\n|-\n| 2017 || [[Kolkata Giltz Fashion Award]] || Best Stylish Actress || For Various Films in 2017 || {{won}} ||\n|-\n| 2017 || [[Accolade Global Film Competition Award]] || Best Actress || Andar Kahini || {{won}}\n|-\n| 2018 || [[Expressions Film Festival]] || Best Actress || Andar Kahini || {{won}}\n|-\n| 2018 || [[Hyderabad Bengali Film Festival]] || Best Actress || Andar Kahini|| {{won}}\n|-\n| 2018 || [[Jharkhand National Film Festival]] || Best Actress || Andar Kahini || {{won}}\n|-\n| 2018 || [[Internation